        "TileImage": "$($repository 5561ba7b-91a6-4403-a351-227015f67c2f).Image",
        "Description": "Hello 47, when searching Lilith Devereux&#39;s phone we found many messages to this &quot;nails&quot; person, it seems like she was using him as a helicopter pilot, the messages sent by Nails shows that he is a member of the cult, and has infection serum on him incase of Lilith&#39;s death, fortunately Nails hasn&#39;t heard of Lilith&#39;s death yet and hasn&#39;t infected himself or anyone, right now he is in Hokkaido at the Gama Facility, working as their helicopter pilot, Eliminate him and take his helicopter, as we have proof of him carrying virus samples in the helicopter, after you take the helicopter fly it to my contact. They will destroy the samples, Good luck, 47. I will leave you to prepare.\r\n\r\nExit: Helicopter\r\n<HCCE>",
